data.description: WHOOMP! THERE IT IS!! (Bonus points if you can name the artist of that song without Binging it.) Don't miss out on your opportunity to own this 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bathroom, charmer with tons of updates and A POOL!! Features include high ceilings and a chandelier that welcome you as you walk through to the wonderfully flowing floor plan. The kitchen has seen several updates, which accompanies the Living Room with fireplace! In addition, the main floor feature a Family Room (currently used as an in-home office) and Dining Room! Upstairs you'll find 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, including your well-finished Owner's Suite! Step outside to find updated landscaping, additional storage, and a fully fenced backyard that features a huge deck and your in-ground pool! All of this and moments away from all your desired amenities! Do not miss out!!
